title: LF Solid Duo partner
body:
Just returning to League setting up everything to get ready to climb back to my original rank in Diamond, Just wanted to find a solid partner to come along for the ride.

Must have Attributes:
1) Positive and never say never attitude
2) Willing to grind 
3) Must work as a team
4) Know what they're doing

Any further questions hit me up

Summoner Name:
Winter Is Back
